 312                  continue 
 313              elif i == 1 and len(clist) > 3 and clist[i + 1] - x == x - clist[0]:

 315                  # and the next one is in the right step

 320                      shortlist.append(str(sub[0] + 1)) 
 321                  else:

 323                          shortlist.append('%d-%d' % (sub[0] + 1, sub[-1] + 1)) 
 324                      else: 
 325                          shortlist.append('%d-%d\\%d' % (sub[0] + 1, sub[-1] + 1, step)) 
 326                  clist = clist[i:] 
 327                  break
